OL,3,CKnife-wielding armed robber caught
OL,4,Cafter being locked inside shop he
OL,5,Ctargeted
OL,7,FCCTV captures the moment that Jordan
OL,8,FPeebles tried to escape but was
OL,9,Fapprehended by police
OL,11,FA knife-wielding armed robber pleaded
OL,12,Fwith police to release him from a
OL,13,FCoventry shop he had targeted after he
OL,14,Fhad been locked inside by a member of
OL,15,Fstaff.
OL,17,FJordan Peebles arrived at a shop in
OL,18,FRiley Square in Coventry on Christmas
OL,19,FEve last year, where he assaulted a
OL,20,Fmember of staff and threatened them
OL,21,Fwith a large kitchen knife.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/5
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
