FL,373,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1773914713
OL,3,CKnife-wielding armed robber caught
OL,4,Cafter being locked inside shop he
OL,5,Ctargeted
OL,7,FWhen the worker left, the 32-year-old
OL,8,Fbegan filling his bags with goods from
OL,9,Fbehind the counter.
OL,11,FWhilst this was happening though, the
OL,12,Fshop worker he had assaulted closed
OL,13,Fthe shutter and locked him inside.
OL,15,FPeebles then tried to force the
OL,16,Fshutter open and realised he was
OL,17,Ftrapped. When police arrived, he
OL,18,Fpleaded to be let out and was arrested
OL,19,Fas soon as he stepped outside.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/5
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
