FL,373,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1773914713
OL,3,CKnife-wielding armed robber caught
OL,4,Cafter being locked inside shop he
OL,5,Ctargeted
OL,7,FAppearing at Warwick Crown Court last
OL,8,Fweek, Peebles pleaded guilty to
OL,9,Frobbery and was handed a prison
OL,10,Fsentence of four years and four months.
OL,12,FDetective Sergeant Jay Aston from
OL,13,FCoventry local CID, said: "This was a
OL,14,Fshocking knifepoint robbery which
OL,15,Fcould have resulted in death or
OL,16,Fserious injury to the man Peebles
OL,17,Fassaulted.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/5
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
