PN,37204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1773914713
OL,3,CKnife-wielding armed robber caught
OL,4,Cafter being locked inside shop he
OL,5,Ctargeted
OL,7,F"The man showed incredible bravery and
OL,8,Fquick thinking to defend himself,
OL,9,Fleave the shop and lower the shutters,
OL,10,Ftrapping Peebles inside.
OL,12,F"I hope Peebles will have time to
OL,13,Freflect on his actions and choices
OL,14,Fwhile in prison and am proud of the
OL,15,Fwork of all the officers involved,
OL,16,Fincluding the response officers who
OL,17,Fwere at the scene within minutes to
OL,18,Farrest him.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/5
